A variety of products and tools available to **treat and care** for your little friends.\n- A wide range of cool accessories for the most **stylish pets** of all.\n- Multiple **locations**, with the ability to upgrade your clinic into the best of the best.\n", "short_description": "Pets & Stuff \u2013 a cute, fun and relaxing game where you become a skilful groomer and veterinarian using a variety of tools, meds and stylish accessories. Let your imagination run wild! \n\nHelp little friends in trouble, make them happy, pampered, clean, well-fed, and while on it - feel free to add a pinch of chic. Enjoy a fully responsive and polished gameplay with different locations to explore, many adorable pets and lots of creativity boosting gadgets to play with."}]}, "developer_name": "HyperVR Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hypervr.games/privacy/petsnstuff.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "HyperVR Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://hypervr.games/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "1990104051447093"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "9685096778184053"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031358_2020302285088213_4522937233069189893_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=om_-b6